title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog

EB: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog. Details: Output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:

2. Check the query result page; observe that no data is returned.
